# ─── Rust / Cargo build artifacts ──────────────────────────────
/target
**/target/

# ─── Tauri (regenerated at build time) ─────────────────────────
/src-tauri/gen/schemas/

# ─── Local models & large binaries (NEVER commit) ──────────────
*.gguf
*.GGUF
*.bin
*.safetensors
*.onnx

# ─── Native runtime binaries (llama.cpp lives in ~/.aismartguy) ─
*.exe
*.dll

# ─── Books / generated reports (avoid committing copyrighted PDFs) ─
# Sample PDFs you DO want tracked must be added with: git add -f path.pdf
*.pdf

# ─── OS / editor cruft ─────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~
__pycache__/

# ─── Internal module instruction blocks (build IP — keep private) ──
/aismartguy modules/
/update_packages/MODULE_SLOT_INSTRUCTIONS.md
/update_packages/nlp_extraction_prompt.txt
